snippet.title: EIGHT Ways To Show How Amber Heard, The ACCUSER Is Actually The ABUSER
snippet.description:
So, I didn't really want to do an actual follow on from my first video 'Why Amber Heard Is The WORST Advocate For Domestic Violence' - but, I felt like I needed to, In this video I go into more detail about Amber's abusive personality, how that comes out in interviews/TV shows, how there have been statements made against her to say she was the violent/aggressive one in the relationship. 

As I have stated in the video, there have been absolutely NO claims made, by Johnny Depp, to say that she DID abuse him, this is simply me going through research and showing you evidence and examples OF her abusive nature. She has gaslighted, manipulated, blackmailed, lied and broke the law. 

Here are all of the links to what I referenced in the video: 

Benicio del Toro statement: http://metro.co.uk/2016/06/09/benicio-del-toro-has-said-some-shocking-things-about-amber-heard-5933643/

Johnny Depp's bodyguard statement: http://hollywoodlife.com/2016/05/31/amber-heard-johnny-depp-bodyguards-no-abuse-claims/

Full Doug Stanhope article: https://www.thewrap.com/johnny-depp-is-being-blackmailed-by-amber-heard-heres-how-i-know-guest-column/

POTC set statement: https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/johnny-depp-amber-heards-rows-8640324

Amber Heard and James Franco Interview: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ffZ93hmelZI

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Overhaulin' full episode: (Unable to find a link to full episode online, but it is in parts on YouTube) 

Amber Heards Arresting Police Officers Statement: Taken from Facebook

Amber Heard Arrested for Domestic Violence against Tasya Van Ree: http://www.tmz.com/2016/06/07/amber-heard-domestic-violence-arrest-partner-tasya-van-ree/

Thanks for watching, please, just to remind you, abusive comments will not be tolerated. I am open to debate but down-right abusive comments will be instantly removed and your account will be reported. 

Thanks to some awesome people on Twitter for the group effort of naming this video! 

If you want to find me on social media: 

Twitter: @autumnonvenus
Instagram: @autumnonvenus
